    - "len(itertools.__doc__) == 1386 — the module docstring has 1386 characters. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.__name__ == 'itertools' (len 9). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.__spec__.__class__.__name__ == 'ModuleSpec' (len 10) — from _frozen_importlib. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
