    - "itertools.__spec__.name == 'itertools' (len 9). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.__spec__.origin == 'built-in' (len 8) — itertools is a built-in C extension module with no file path. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.__loader__ is the BuiltinImporter class itself (type); its __name__ == 'BuiltinImporter' (len 15). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.__loader__.__class__.__name__ == 'type' — BuiltinImporter is a class. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

